## 🚨 What To Do If You Are a Victim

| Action | Details |
|--------|---------|
| **Call immediately** | Cyber Crime Helpline — **1930** (24×7, Free) |
| **Report online** | [cybercrime.gov.in](https://cybercrime.gov.in) |
| **Block the fraudster** | Block the number on WhatsApp and report it |
| **Inform your bank** | Call your bank's helpline to freeze the transaction if possible |
| **Save all evidence** | Take screenshots of messages, UPI transaction IDs, and call logs |

