## 📋 Quick Self-Check Before Any Online Transaction

```
Before sending money or sharing details online — ask yourself:

  ✔  Do I personally know this person or organization?
  ✔  Did I initiate this request or did it come out of nowhere?
  ✔  Is there unnecessary urgency or pressure to act fast?
  ✔  Am I being asked to pay to receive something?
  ✔  Does this feel too good to be true?

If even ONE answer is suspicious → STOP. Don't proceed.
Call 1930 if in doubt.
```

